{"tid":1656002,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"發過夢既呢排去泰國小心為上","createTime":"2019-10-15T10:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T07:55:51.000Z","uid":271714,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d7707752683231cd12fe2b75eeeddd39f1af326a","tid":1656002,"uid":271714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:55:08.000Z","msg":"背景: 老婆泰國華人, 我地住Pathum Thani. <br />\n<br />\n近排去續居留，平時counter搞掂，今次個移民官叫我入房，問有無香港既protestor諗住響泰國示威? 我話我點知(不過前排曼谷確係有香港人舉遮)。 佢話咁好啦，不過招呼外國人住一定要報比警察 (好似大陸以前報戶口咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) 如果唔係個居留就有影響喇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加埋近日陸軍國安中心係咁召D華商開會呼籲督灰，發過夢既真係要諗下10-11月唔去，因為11月係教宗訪泰，又有東盟大會，呢排D官相當之緊張，係咪都抽秤下先，費事出事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7f217f1c2e3bb50ad4bf1efaa0a9c0000906af8","tid":1656002,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:59:25.000Z","msg":"好人好者真係盡量唔好去泰國 越南 菲律賓"},{"pid":"1bcd3686453863a4294014bbfe0be0b61b597298","tid":1656002,"uid":54359,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b7f217f1c2e3bb50ad4bf1efaa0a9c0000906af8","tid":1656002,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:59:25.000Z","msg":"好人好者真係盡量唔好去泰國 越南 菲律賓"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T19:04:10.000Z","msg":"越南唔奶共架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n泰國，菲律賓，馬來西亞，印尼就奶至雪雪聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e11265d7e6683d8021fafd5ec8bc3a3091460b1","tid":1656002,"uid":238011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T19:05:02.000Z","msg":"仆街下星期要去 有事做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry